Description:
xstrerror() function: return diagnostic string based on error code.
Multithread-safe. With out-of-memory checking.

Files:
lib/xstrerror.h
lib/xstrerror.c

Depends-on:
gettext-h
gnulib-i18n
strerror_r-posix
xalloc
xvasprintf

configure.ac:

Makefile.am:
lib_SOURCES += xstrerror.c

Include:
"xstrerror.h"

Link:
$(LTLIBINTL) when linking with libtool, $(LIBINTL) otherwise

License:
GPL

Maintainer:
all
